{"tid":2490062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿里巴巴遭重罰後首露面！2小時會議馬雲「全程靜默喝茶」","createTime":"2021-04-15T10:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T10:40:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb57298d4b0544dc34dc6bab5ec42da237edc9d","tid":2490062,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111748-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111748-PH.jpg&h=9e4d3a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲14日出席俄羅斯總統普丁（Vladimir Putin）召開的視訊會議，而這<br />\n也是他在阿里巴巴遭中國市場監管總局重罰182.28億元人民幣（約新台幣791.6億元）後<br />\n首度露面；據了解會議共2小時，但馬雲全程靜默、沒有發言，僅偶爾喝茶。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯衞星通訊社報導，馬雲周三參加俄羅斯地理學會監事會（Russian<br />\nGeographical Society）視訊會議，他坐在一個背景有梅花、充滿中國風的辦公室裡，過<br />\n程中沒有參與討論和發言，只是在一旁靜靜聆聽其他人報告、偶爾舉起杯子喝茶。<br />\n <br />\n中國監管部門本月10日表示，經調查發現自2015年以來，阿里巴巴集團濫用該市場支配地<br />\n位、對平台內商家提出「二選一」要求，禁止平台內商家在競爭對手的平台開店或參加促<br />\n銷活動，並藉助市場力量、平台規則和數據、算法等技術手段，增強自身市場力量，獲取<br />\n不正當競爭優勢。<br />\n <br />\n監管總局指出，阿里巴巴此舉已違反《反壟斷法》第十七條第一款第（四）項「禁止沒有<br />\n正當理由，限定交易相對人只能與其進行交易」，故依法作出行政處罰決定，處以其2019<br />\n年中國境內銷售額人民幣4557.12億元4%的罰款，共計人民幣182.28億元，為實施反壟斷<br />\n法以來最大金額罰款。<br />\n <br />\n阿里巴巴在收到《國家市場監督管理總局行政處罰決定書》後，隨即發聲明強調對此處罰<br />\n誠懇接受、堅決服從，並將「強化依法經營，進一步加強合規體系建設，立足創新發展，<br />\n更好履行社會責任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pse.is/3e2rpt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2F3e2rpt&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=27059121\" target=\"_blank\">https://pse.is/3e2rpt</a>"},{"pid":"dbdc7ae95ff40e88662b1f05417336a092ba978c","tid":2490062,"uid":19213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:29:58.000Z","msg":"咁似范冰冰單野<br />\n今次馬雲要俾幾多高層無套中出先出得黎呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3230371a7caeb7a02a676baff2fcbaa339cdf425","tid":2490062,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:35:19.000Z","msg":"其實係咪替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ad74c18b33ee17410e63d8ab37180551c7e355","tid":2490062,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3230371a7caeb7a02a676baff2fcbaa339cdf425","tid":2490062,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:35:19.000Z","msg":"其實係咪替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"應該隔離有個人望住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0153d798d41a60fc394316f4290e7f56daf6cc","tid":2490062,"uid":225422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbdc7ae95ff40e88662b1f05417336a092ba978c","tid":2490062,"uid":19213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:29:58.000Z","msg":"咁似范冰冰單野<br />\n今次馬雲要俾幾多高層無套中出先出得黎呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"比習近平個女用假鳩屌"},{"pid":"ccb7cfea15fb9dd8021d75de191bfece365b5162","tid":2490062,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3230371a7caeb7a02a676baff2fcbaa339cdf425","tid":2490062,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:35:19.000Z","msg":"其實係咪替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"播片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}